  "description": "Fill your New York City stay with style at Battery Park. Your Sonder will be on floors 3\u20139 and includes a modern kitchen. Savor the view of this magical city from the seasonal rooftop pool. There's a fitness center, golf simulator, and co-working space. Why not have it all with endless amenities and an incredible location? You'll be across from The Battery \u2014 a beautiful waterfront oasis. The New York Stock Exchange, Wall Street, and One World Trade Center are also a short walk away.The spaceWe\u2019re here to help navigate your stay from start to finish. Check in. Request amenities. Connect to WiFi. Contact customer support. Whatever you need, we\u2019ve got you covered.\n\nThis Sonder has a front desk which is staffed 24/7. Our on-site team is available to ensure you have a better stay.\n\n- Contact-free check-in\n- 24/7 virtual support\n- Super-fast WiFi\n- Fresh towels and bathroom essentials\n- Housekeeping services available on-demand for a nominal fee\n- In-suite laundry\n- Fully equipped kitchen\n- Chromecast for streaming\n- Seasonal rooftop pool\n- Fitness center\n- Co-working space\n- Music studio\n- Golf simulator room\n- Luggage lockers (first available)\n- Limited paid street parking available\n\nWhat\u2019s nearby\n- 5 minute walk to Antica Ristorante (tableside preparations of classic Italian dishes)\n- 8 minute walk to The Dead Rabbit (Redbreast 12, neat, at this iconic Irish bar)\n- 10 minute subway to Takahachi Bakery (try the matcha crepe, thank us later)\n- 10 minute walk to One World Trade Center (stunning 360-degree views from the observation deck)\n\nWe have multiple spaces at this property, each designed to give you a beautiful place to stay \u2014 while our style is consistent, the view, layout, and design may vary.\n\nGuests can book housekeeping services on-demand for a nominal fee. This ensures you can enjoy an uninterrupted and environmentally sustainable stay. Housekeeping services must be scheduled 24 hours in advance.Other things to note- There's no cable\n- The pool is open from Memorial Day to Labor Day, yearly\n- You may hear construction noise from renovations nearby\n- This building briefly tests the fire alarms on the last Friday of each month. We apologize for any inconvenienceRegistration numberExempt",
