    "htmlText": "Fill your New York City stay with style at Battery Park. Your Sonder will be on floors 3\u20139 and includes a modern kitchen. Savor the view of this magical city from the seasonal rooftop pool. There's a fitness center, golf simulator, and co-working space. Why not have it all with endless amenities and an incredible location? You'll be across from The Battery \u2014 a beautiful waterfront oasis. The New York Stock Exchange, Wall Street, and One World Trade Center are also a short walk away.<br /><br /><b>The space</b><br />We\u2019re here to help navigate your stay from start to finish. Check in. Request amenities. Connect to WiFi. Contact customer support. Whatever you need, we\u2019ve got you covered.\r<br />\r<br />This Sonder has a front desk which is staffed 24/7. Our on-site team is available to ensure you have a better stay.\r<br />\r<br />- Contact-free check-in\r<br />- 24/7 virtual support\r<br />- Super-fast WiFi\r<br />- Fresh towels and bathroom essentials\r<br />- Housekeeping services available on-demand for a nominal fee\r<br />- In-suite laundry\r<br />- Fully equipped kitchen\r<br />- Chromecast for streaming\r<br />- Seasonal rooftop pool\r<br />- Fitness center\r<br />- Co-working space\r<br />- Music studio\r<br />- Golf simulator room\r<br />- Luggage lockers (first available)\r<br />- Limited paid street parking available\r<br />\r<br /><b>What\u2019s nearby</b>\r<br />- 5 minute walk to Antica Ristorante (tableside preparations of classic Italian dishes)\r<br />- 8 minute walk to The Dead Rabbit (Redbreast 12, neat, at this iconic Irish bar)\r<br />- 10 minute subway to Takahachi Bakery (try the matcha crepe, thank us later)\r<br />- 10 minute walk to One World Trade Center (stunning 360-degree views from the observation deck)\r<br />\r<br />We have multiple spaces at this property, each designed to give you a beautiful place to stay \u2014 while our style is consistent, the view, layout, and design may vary.\r<br />\r<br />Guests can book housekeeping services on-demand for a nominal fee. This ensures you can enjoy an uninterrupted and environmentally sustainable stay. Housekeeping services must be scheduled 24 hours in advance.<br /><br /><b>Other things to note</b><br />- There's no cable\r<br />- The pool is open from Memorial Day to Labor Day, yearly\r<br />- You may hear construction noise from renovations nearby\r<br />- This building briefly tests the fire alarms on the last Friday of each month. We apologize for any inconvenience<br /><br /><b>Registration number</b><br />Exempt",
